st to ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀;␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀      spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to<␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     e spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀<␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     e spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀␀=␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     he spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀=␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     he spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀>␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀>␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀?␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀      the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀?␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀      the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to@␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     n the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     n the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀␀A␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     un the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀A␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     un the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀B␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀B␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀C␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀      run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀C␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀      run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request toD␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     y run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     y run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀␀E␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     ly run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀E␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     ly run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀F␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     ely run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀F␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     ely run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀G␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     tely run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀G␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     tely run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request toH␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     ately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀H␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     ately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀␀I␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     iately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀I␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     iately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀J␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     diately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀J␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     diately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀K␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     ediately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀K␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     ediately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request toL␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     mediately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀L␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     mediately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀␀M␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     mmediately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀M␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     mmediately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀␀N␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀     immediately run the spool queue.  Now the process sends a request to␀ ␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀?␀␀␀␀␀E␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀     duties of the 'handle the jobs in the spool queue' process.␀␀/␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀     duties of the 'handle the spool queue ␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀)␀␀␀␀␀/␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀     duties of the 'handle the spool queue␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀F␀␀␀␀␀L␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀     the job the process would then call Do_queue_jobs() to take on the␀␀␀/␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀     the job the process would then try to ␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀$␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀/␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀     the job the process would then try to␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀     the job the process␀␀␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀     would then try to ␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀     the job the process␀␀P␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀     process to handle job reception;  in previous versions after receiving␀␀␀L␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀     process to handle job reception;  in previous versions the process␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀<␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀     would then try toL␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀     process to handle job reception;  in previous versions the process␀␀␀^␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀     process to handle job reception;  in previous versions the process would then try to␀ ␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀G␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀^␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀     process to handle job reception;  in previous versions the process would then try to␀␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀     process to handleL␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀     job reception;  in previous versions the process would then try to␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀     process to handle␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀      process to handle␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀      process to handle␀␀␀N␀␀␀␀(␀␀␀     When you send a job via LPR, the LPD server forks a 'service socket'␀`␀␀␀␀(␀␀␀     When you send a job via LPR, the LPD server forks a 'service ␀␀␀b␀␀␀␀␀␀a␀␀␀␀␀␀`␀␀␀␀␀␀_␀␀␀␀␀␀^␀␀␀␀␀␀]␀␀␀␀␀␀\␀␀␀␀␀␀[␀␀␀␀␀␀Z␀␀␀␀␀␀Y␀␀␀␀␀␀X␀␀␀␀␀␀W␀␀␀z␀␀␀V␀␀␀~␀␀␀U␀␀␀␀␀␀T␀␀␀}␀␀␀S␀␀␀␀␀␀R␀␀␀␀␀␀Q␀␀␀␀␀␀P␀␀␀␀␀␀O␀␀␀␀␀␀N␀␀␀␀␀␀M␀␀␀␀␀␀L␀␀␀x␀␀␀K␀␀␀|␀␀␀J␀␀␀␀␀␀I␀␀␀␀␀␀H␀␀␀␀␀␀G␀␀␀␀␀␀F␀␀␀␀␀␀E␀␀␀␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀␀C␀␀␀␀␀␀B␀␀␀␀␀␀A␀␀␀␀␀␀@␀␀␀x␀␀␀?␀␀␀␀␀␀>␀␀␀␀␀␀=␀␀␀␀␀␀<␀␀␀␀␀␀;␀␀␀u␀␀␀:␀␀␀␀␀␀9␀␀␀␀␀␀8␀␀␀~␀␀␀7␀␀␀␀␀␀6␀␀␀␀␀␀5␀␀␀␀␀␀4␀␀␀␀␀␀3␀␀␀␀␀␀2␀␀␀␀␀␀1␀␀␀␀␀␀0␀␀␀␀␀␀/␀␀␀␀␀␀.␀␀␀␀␀␀-␀␀␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀␀␀␀(␀␀␀␀␀␀'␀␀␀␀␀␀&␀␀␀␀␀␀%␀␀␀␀␀␀$␀␀␀␀␀␀#␀␀␀␀␀␀"␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀~␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀|␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀^␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀xterm|vs100|xterm terminal emulator (X window system)␀OH␀OF␀␀␀OP␀OQ␀OR␀OS␀>[?1;3;4;5l[?7;8h[1;65r[65;1H␀>[?1;3;4;5l[?7;8h␀[2~␀[6~␀[5~␀[17~␀[18~␀[19~␀[20~␀[21~␀[15~␀[?25h␀[?25l␀[23~␀[24~␀[@␀[%p1%d@␀[%p1%dX␀[L␀[M␀[P␀[%p1%dL␀[%p1%dM␀[%p1%dP␀[B␀[H[J␀D␀(0␀(B␀[%i%p1%d;%p2%dH␀[C␀[A␀E␀[K␀[J␀[7m␀[m␀[4m␀[m␀[1m␀[7m␀[5m␀[m␀M␀7␀8␀[%i%p1%d;%p2%dr␀[%p1%dA␀[%p1%dB␀[%p1%dC␀[%p1%dD␀[3g␀H␀␀/usr/share/tabset/vt100␀[H␀``aaffggjjkkllmmnnooppqqrrssttuuvvwwxxyyzz{{||␀[?1h=␀[?1l>␀OA␀OB␀OC␀OD␀OM␀Oq␀Or␀Os␀Op␀On␀ ␀␀␀[?7l␀[?7h␀>[?1;3;4;5l[?7;8h␀40-m8␀1620-m8|1640-m8|diablo 1620 w/8 column left margin: :do=^J:co#124:is=\r        \E9: :do=^J:ct=\E2:st=\E1:ch=\E\t%i%.:   :if=/usr/share/tabset/xerox1720:    :kb=^H:le=^H:bs:co#132:hc:hu=\EU:hd=\ED:os:pt:up=\E\n:␀1620-m8|1640-m8|diab␀m2-nam|minitel|minitel-2|minitel-2-nam|minitel 2|France Telecom Minitel:    :li#24:al=\E[L:dl=\E[M:ip=7:dc=\E[P:ei=\E[4l:im=\E[4h:xn:   :ho=\E[H:cl=\E[H\E[J:ug#0:sg#0: :co#80:am@:bs:c␀r   ␀␀␀␀␀t   ␀␀␀␀␀v   ␀␀␀␀␀x   ␀␀␀␀␀z   ␀␀␀␀␀|   ␀␀␀␀␀~   ␀␀␀␀␀P   ␀␀␀␀␀R   ␀␀␀␀␀T   ␀␀␀␀␀V   ␀␀␀␀␀X   ␀␀␀␀␀Z   ␀␀␀␀␀\   ␀␀␀␀␀^   ␀␀␀␀␀`␀␀␀␀␀b␀␀␀␀␀d␀␀␀␀␀f␀␀␀␀␀h␀␀␀␀␀j␀␀␀␀␀l␀␀␀␀␀n␀␀␀␀␀p␀␀␀␀␀r␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀v␀␀␀␀␀x␀␀␀␀␀z␀␀␀␀␀|␀␀␀␀␀~␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀NF:se=^NG:ta=43\t:ma=^Z^P:cd=6^N@^V:␀mdl110|cybernex mdl-110it2|intertube2|intertec data systems intertube 2it2␀it2|intertube2|intertec data systems intertube 2: :do=^J:am:bs:cl=^L:co#80:ho=^A:li#25:up=^Z:ce=\EK:  :cm=^N%+ %+ :ch=^P%\102%.:cv=^K%.:nd=^F:do=\n:ll=^K^X\r:    :so=\E0P:se=\E0@:␀it2|intertube2|intertec data systems intertube 2virtual|VIRTUAL|cb unix virtual terminalVIRTUALvirtual|VIRTUAL|cb unix virtual terminalvirtual␀apollo:  :al=\EI:am:bs:cd=\EJ:ce=\EK:ch=\EN%d:cl=^L:cm=\EM%+ %d␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀107%r%.%.:nd=\E\103:  :up=\E\101:ce=\E\113:cd=\E\114:al=\E\120:dl=\E\116:ic=\E\117:   :da:db:kl=\E\104:kr=\E\103:ku=\E\101:kd=\E\102:kh=\E\105:   :so=\E\141\004:seregent25|Adds Regent 25regent25regent|Adds Regent SeriesAdds Regent Seriesintext|Interactive Systems Corporation modified owl 1200Interactive Systems Corporation modified owl 1200intext|Interactive Systems Corporation modified owl 1200intext4404|tek440444044113-nd|tek4113-nd|tektronix 4113 color graphics, no dialog areatek4113-nd␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀"␀␀␀␀␀$␀␀␀␀␀&␀␀␀␀␀(␀␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀.␀␀␀␀␀0␀␀␀␀␀2␀␀␀␀␀4␀␀␀␀␀6␀␀␀␀␀8␀␀␀␀␀:␀␀␀␀␀<␀␀␀␀␀>␀␀␀␀␀@␀␀␀␀␀B␀␀␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀F␀␀␀␀␀H␀␀␀␀EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[J:   :es:hs:i2=\E7\E[?6l\E[2K\E[?6h\E8:ts=\E7\E[?6l\E[2K\E[;%i%df:   :fs=\E[?6h\E8:ds=\E7\E[?6l\E[2K\E[?6h\E8:   :ti=\E[?6l\E[H\E[J:te=\E[?6h\E%!0\ELBP0\E%!1\E[32;1f:   :is=\E%!0\ELBP0\E%!1\E[H\E[2g\EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[8C\EH\E[J:   :li#32:do=^J:al=3\E[L:xn:am:le=^H:bs:cd=\E[J:   :ce=5\E[K:cl=156\E[H\E[J:cm=\E[%i%d;%dH:co#80:dc=4\E[P:dl=3\E[M:    :ho=\E[H:ic=4\E[@:md=\E[1m:mr=\E[7m:mb=\E[5m:me=\E[m:ku=\EM:    ␀␀␀␀␀P␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀    ,␀e␀,␀␀␀#   ␀#   ␀$   PB   ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀H␀␀␀␀␀␀@B␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀-␀␀␀-␀␀␀-␀␀␀-␀␀␀@B␀@B␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@B␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@B␀@B␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@B␀@B␀␀␀␀␀*1␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀>␀␀␀<␀␀␀^␀␀␀v␀␀␀␀␀␀␀#␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀`␀@␀a␀@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀f␀@␀g␀@␀#␀␀␀#␀␀␀j␀@␀k␀@␀l␀@␀m␀@␀n␀@␀o␀@␀p␀@␀q␀@␀r␀@␀s␀@␀t␀@␀u␀@␀v␀@␀w␀@␀x␀@␀y␀@␀z␀@␀{␀@␀|␀@␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀*( *((*(4*(<*(\2(␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@B   ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀   ␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀te:  :al=\E[L:am:bs:cd=\E[J:ce=\E[K:cl=^L:cm=\E[%i%d;%dH:co#88:  :dc=\E[P:dl=\E[M:do=\E[B:ho=\E[H:ic=\E[@:li#32: :nd=\E[C:ms:pt:so=\E[7m:se=\E[m:us=\E[4m:ue=\E[m:up=\E[A:   :kb=^h:ku=\E[A:kd=\E[B:kl=\E[D:kr=\E[C:eo:is=\E>\E[0m^L:    :GS=\E[11m:GE=\E[10m:GV=\140:GH=a:G1=c:G2=f:G3=e:G4=d:GU=u: :GD=s:GC=b:GL=v:GR=t:CO=\E[5l:CF=\E[5h:␀lisa|apple lisa console display, black on white␀v50|visual 50:  :am:bs:al=\EL:dl=\EM:   :cd=\Ek:ce=\EK:cl=^Z:cm=\E=%+\040%+\040:co#80:do=^J:ho=\EH: :kb=^H:kd=\EB:kh=\EH:kl=\ED:kr=\EC:ku=\EA:li#24:ms:nd=^L:pt:    :so=\EU:se=\ET:up=^K:␀v50|visual 50wy75-wvb|wyse75-wvb|wyse 75 with visual bell 132 columns␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀1␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀;␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀"␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀E␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀  ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀F␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀I␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀G␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀J␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀<␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀F␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀H␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀G␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀K␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀I␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀I␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀F␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀J␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀J␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀J␀␀␀␀␀!␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀3␀␀␀␀␀"␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀#␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀G␀␀␀␀␀$␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀O␀␀␀␀␀%␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀#␀␀␀␀␀&␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀'␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀(␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀F␀␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀B␀␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀?␀␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀2:   :is=\E%\014\014\014\016\003\000\003\002\003\002\000\000\000\000\000\000\000\000\000\000\000:    :al=\EE:am:bs:bt=\EI:cd=\Ey:ce=\Et:cl=\E+:cm=\000\E=%+ %+ :co#80:   :dc=\EW:dl=\ER:do=^J:ho=^^:ic=\EQ:  :k1=\001@\015:k2=\001A\015:k3=\001B\015:k4=\001C\015:   :k5=\001D\015:k6=\001E\015:k7=\001F\015:kn#7:   :ko=ho:l1=F1:l2=F2:l3=F3:l4=F4:l5=F5:l6=F6:l7=F7:   :kb=^H:kd=^J:kh=^^:kl=^H:kr=^L:ku=^K:li#24: :ma=j^Jk^P^K^Pl ^R^L^L :nd=^L:se=\E(:so=\E):ta=\Ei:up=^K:␀adm22|22|lsi adm22␀h19-bs|h19bs|heathkit w/keypad shifted:    :ks=\Et:ke=\Eu: :al=1*\EL:am:le=^H:bs:cd=\EJ:ce=\EK:cl=\EE:cm=\EY%+ %+ :co#80:dc=\EN:   :dl=1*\EM:do=\EB:ei=\EO:ho=\EH:im=\E@:li#24:mi:nd=\EC:as=\EF:ae=\EG:    :ms:pt:sr=\EI:se=\Eq:so=\Ep:up=\EA:vs=\Ex4:ve=\Ey4: :kb=^h:ku=\EA:kd=\EB:kl=\ED:kr=\EC:kh=\EH:kn#8:ke=\E>:ks=\E=:   :k1=\ES:k2=\ET:k3=\EU:k4=\EV:k5=\EW:    :l6=blue:l7=red:l8=white:k6=\EP:k7=\EQ:k8=\ER:  :es:hs:ts=\Ej\Ex5\Ex1\EY8%+ \Eo:fs=\Ek\Ey5:ds=\Ey1:␀h19-bs|h19bs|heathkit w/keypad shifted2392|hp2392|hp23[43B![KK[B [6@ empty[6;65Hissues[B  of queue starting,  polling the queues for done jobs, and other [B  issues.  A small side effect of this is that the LPD server process[B  now starts printing processes.  This is actually beneficial as it can[B  now limit the total number of printing processes and allow some[B  LPQ/LPC/LPR etc actions. Here is a summary of the current operation[B [18P[14;65Hwhen there[15;7H  is most likely no reason to.  Used when you have some REALLY odd[16;5H    programs running that will directly manipulate the LPD spool queues[17;5H    and you do not want to have to connect to the server. [18;5H    (default is OFF).[K[19;5H lpd_poll_time - interval[41@ in secs between checking queues for work[20;6H   Done if there is some reason to suspect that some spool queue[21;6H   had problems and might need to be restarted.  This also handles a[22;5H    race condition where a job arrives just as the process servicing[23;5H    the spool queue exits.[K[24;5H    (default is 5 minutes)[K[25;5H lpd_poll_start_interval - if there are spool queues which need service,[26;5H    fork up to 'lpd_poll_servers_started' processes at a time and then[27;6H   wait for lpd_poll_start_interval seconds before forking more.[28;6H   This prevents the deadly situation where the LPD server is started[29;5H    and in turn  starts a gizillion process; the rc starupt scripts[30;5H    may fail because there are no free processes (I kid you not on this[31;5H    one, it drove me nuts trying to find out why the system would crash[32;5H    ONLY when LPD ran with NO debugging - the IO cau[18@sed it to slow dow[33;5H    enough so that the other scripts could run).[K[34;5H    (default now 1 second)[K[35;5H lpd_poll_servers_started - maximum number of processs to fork to be[36;5H    spool queue servers at a time.  this prevents the massive forking a huge[37;5H    number of processes at once.[K[38;5H    (default[6@ now 5[39;6H[K[BWhen you send a job via LPR, the LPD server forks a 'service socket'[41;5Hprocess to handle job reception;  in previous versions after receiving[42;5Hthe job the process would then call Do_queue_jobs() to take on the[43;5Hduties of the 'handle the jobs in the spool queue' process.  In[B6308[44;20H513[Hto[42;6Hthe LPD server to run a process to do this work.  Similarly, the[43;6HLPD server forks a process to handle LPC operations;  lpc start[HF:do=^J:ho=\EY  :␀regent25|Adds Regent 254404|tek4404tek4404␀tek4125: :ks=\E=:li#34:  :is=\E%\!0\EQD1\EUX03\EKA\ELBB2\ELCE0\ELI100\ELJ2\ELLB2\ELM0\ELS1\ELX00\ELV1\E%\!1\E>\E[?3l\E[?4l\E[?5l\E[?7h\E[?8h:dl=\E[1M:   :al=\E[1L:cs@:sc@:rc@:im=\E1:   :do=2\E[B:co#80:li#24:cl=50\E[H\E[J:sf=2*\ED:   :le=^H:bs:am:cm=5\E[%i%d;%dH:nd=2\E[C:up=2\E[A: :ce=3\E[K:cd=50\E[J:so=2\E[7m:se=2\E[m:us=2\E[4m:ue=2\E[m:  :md=2\E[1m:mr=2\E[7m:mb=2\E[5m:me=2\E[m:    :is=\E>\E[?1;3;4;5l\E[?7;8h\E[1;24r\E[24;1H:    :if=/usr/share/tabset/vt100:nw=2\EE:ho=\E[H:    :as=2\E(0:ae=2\E(B: :ac=``aaffggjjkkllmmnnooppqqrrssttuuvvwwxxyyzz{{||: :rs=\E>\E[?1;3;4;5l\E[?7;8h:ks=\E[?1h\E=:ke=\E[?1l\E>:  :ku=\EOA:kd=\EOB:kr=\EOC:kl=\EOD:kb=\177:   :k0=\EOy:k1=\EOP:k2=\EOQ:k3=\EOR:k4=\EOS:k5=\EOt:   :k6=\EOu:k7=\EOv:k8=\EOl:k9=\EOw:k;=\EOx:@8=\EOM:   :K1=\EOq:K2=\EOr:K3=\EOs:K4=\EOp:K5=\EOn:pt:sr=2*\EM:xn:    :sc=2\E7:rc=2\E8:cs=5\E[%i%d;%dr:UP=2\E[%dA:DO=2\E[%dB:RI=2\E[%dC:  :LE=2\E[%dD:ct=2\E[3g:st=2\EH:ta=^I:ms:bl=^G:cr=^M:eo:it#8: :RA=\E[?7l:SA=\E[?7h:␀tek41254107-s|tek4107-s|Tektronix 4107 with sysline but no memorytek4107-stek4107|tek4207|4107|4207|Tektronix 4107 graphics terminal with memorytek4107tek4025a|4025a|Tektronix 4025Atek4025atek4013|4013|tektronix 4013tektronix 4013␀pcvt32hw|dec vt220 with HP-fkey labels, 32 lines and 132 cols: :li#32: :co#132:    :Xs:    :is=\E>\E[?3l\E[?4l\E[?5l\E[?7h\E[?8h\E[1;32r\E[32;1H:  :   :AL=\E[%dL: :DC=\E[%dP: :DL=\E[%dM: :DO=\E[%dB: :IC=\E[%d@: :LE=\E[%dD: :RI=\E[%dC: :SF=\E[%dS: :SR=\E[%dT: :UP=\E[%dA:        :ac=llmmkkjjuuttvvwwqqxxnnpprr``aa:  :ae=^O: :al=\E[L:   :am:    :as=^N: :bl=^G: :bs:    :cb=\E[1K:  :cd=\E[J:   :ce=\E[K:   :cl=\E[H\E[J:   :cm=\E[%i%d;%d ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀g␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀m␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀u␀␀␀n␀␀␀n␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀i␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀i␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀l␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀i␀␀␀p␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀\E[m: :mi:    :mr=\E[7m:  :ms:    :nd=\E[C:   :pb#16000000:   :pt:    :rc=\E8:    :rf=/usr/share/tabset/vt100:    :rs=\Ec\E>\E[? ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀y␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀: :DL=\E[%dM: :DO=\E[%dB: :IC=\E[%d@: :LE=\E[%dD: :RI=\E[%dC: :SF=\E[%dS: :SR=\E[%dT: :UP=\E[%dA:        :ac ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀O␀␀␀F␀␀␀F␀␀␀)␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀E[5~: :kb=\177:   :kd=\EOB:   :ke=\E[?1l\E>:  :kh=\E[1~:  :kl=\EOD:   :km:    :kr=\EOC:   :ks=\E[?1h\E=:  :ku=\EOA:   :le=^H ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀t␀␀␀w␀␀␀e␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀k␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ann arbor ambassador/48 lines in reverse videoann arbor ambassador/48 lines in reverse videoaaa-48-s|ann ar ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀D␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ah1520|hazeltine 1520h1520dt80w|dmdt80w|dm80w|datamedia dt80/1 in 132 char modedm80wb610|610|610bct|tty61 ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀l␀␀␀e␀␀␀m␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀i␀␀␀g␀␀␀h␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀T␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀l␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L:    :se=\EG0:so=\EG1:up=^K:us=\EG1:ue=\EG0:␀adm31|31|lsi adm31␀tvi924vb|924vb|televideo model 924 visual bell ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀:k9=^AH\r: :k0=^AI\r:ko=ic,dc,al,dl,cl,ce,cd,bt:sr=\Ej:    :hs:fs=^Y\Es1:ts=\Ef:ds=\Es0\Ef^Y:␀tvi924vb|924vb|te ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀x␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀=\EOS:  :al=\E[L:dl=\E[M:ic=\E[@:dc=\E[P:   :AL=\E[%dL:DL=\E[%dM:IC=\E[%d@:DC=\E[%dP:␀sun-34|Sun 34-line window ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀5␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀left margin1640-lm1640|1740|630|1730|x1700|diablo|xerox|diablo 16406301620-m8|1640-m8|diablo 1620 w/8 colu ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀_␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀mtron ABM 85abm85wy85|wyse85|wyse 85wy85wy60-nt|wyse60-nt|Wyse 60 with broken tab supportwyse60-nttvi912- ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀ ␀␀␀u␀␀␀p␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀'␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀'␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀eii|microterm mime1mime-fb|full bright mime1mime-fbz29a|z29a-kc-bc|h29a-kc-bc|heath/zenith 29 in ansi mode ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀a␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀_␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ vt420 7 bit controls 132x24 autowrap␀vt420-w|DEC vt420 7 bit controls 132x24 autowrap:        :co#132:      ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀T␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀a␀␀␀d␀␀␀l␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀u␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀>\E[?1h\E F\E[?4l:        :k1=\EOP:k2=\EOQ:k3=\EOR:k4=\EOS:k6=\E[17~:k7=\E[18~:        :k8=\E[19~:k9=\E[20~: ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀u␀␀␀r␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀g␀␀␀i␀␀␀z␀␀␀i␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀;␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀c␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀u␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀c␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t300-pf|dec-vt340-pf|dec vt320 with PF1-PF4dec-vt340-pfvt320|vt300|vt340|vt320 with status linevt300vt200- ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀i␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀I␀␀␀ ␀␀␀k␀␀␀i␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀y␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i#66:hc:hu=\EL:hd=\EK:so=\E[1m:se=\E[22m:    :us=\E[4m:ue=\E[24m:␀ln03|dec ln03 LaserPrintervt125|vt125-am|DEC ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀r␀␀␀y␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀y␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀m␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀=^I:  :AF=\E[3%dm:AB=\E[4%dm:op=\E[39;49m:sc=\E7:rc=\E8:  :k1=\E[M:k2=\E[N:k3=\E[O:k4=\E[P:k5=\E[Q:k6=\E[R:k7= ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀O␀␀␀N␀␀␀L␀␀␀Y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀N␀␀␀O␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀b␀␀␀u␀␀␀g␀␀␀g␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀I␀␀␀O␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀l␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀no: :li#50: :pa@:Co@:AF@:AB@:AX@:op@:us=\E[4m:ue=\E[24m:    :ac=f\260g\261}\243+\253,\273i\247: :   :am:bs:NP:ms: ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀g␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀c␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀u␀␀␀n␀␀␀)␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀\E[H:ku=\E[A:kd=\E[B:kl=\E[D:kr=\E[C:le=^H:sf=\E[S:sr=\E[T:    :kN=\E[G:kP=\E[I:@7=\E[F:kI=\E[L:kD=\177:kB=\E[Z ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀1␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l=\E[M:do=\E[B:bt=\E[Z:ho=\E[H:ic=\E[@:cb=\E[1K:    :nd=\E[C:rs=\Ec:so=\E[7m:se=\E[27m:up=\E[A:cr=^M:ta=^I: :AF ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀x␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i%dd:ch=\E[%i%d`:    :mb=\E[5m:md=\E[1m:mr=\E[7m:me=\E[m:bl=^G:␀cons50l1|cons50-iso8859-1cons50-m|ansil-mono|a ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀u␀␀␀g␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d=\E[C:rs=\Ec:so=\E[7m:se=\E[27m:up=\E[A:cr=^M:ta=^I: :AF=\E[3%dm:AB=\E[4%dm:op=\E[39;49m:sc=\E7:rc=\E8:  :k1 ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀[m:bl=^G:␀cons50-m|ansil-mono|ansi80x50-monoc100-s|concept-s|concept100-s|slow concept 100concept100-s␀8686 ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀5␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀=\EE:nd=\EC: :cm=\EF%+ %+ :up=\EA:do=\EB:ho=\EH:bt=\E>:  :al=\EL:dc=\EP:dl=\EM:ei=\E@:im=\EQ:mi: :kl=\ED:kr=\ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀rse video:  :md=\E[1;7m:mr=\E[m:mb=\E[5;7m:mk=\E[7;8m:me=\E[7m: :us=\E[4;7m:ue=\E[7m:se=\E[7m:so=\E[m:  :is=\E ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀W␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀y␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀ ␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀R␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀'␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀k␀␀␀e␀␀␀t␀␀␀'␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀80:   :dc=4\E[P:dl=3\E[M:ho=\E[H:ic=4\E[@:    :md=\E[1m:mr=\E[7m:mb=\E[5m:mk=\E[8m:me=\E[m:   :ku=\EM:kd=\ED:kl=\E[ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀l␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀;␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀f␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀i␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀assador|ann arbor ambassador/30 linesambassadorzen30|z30|zentec 30z30␀apollo_color|apollo color display:  :d ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀D␀␀␀o␀␀␀_␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀_␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀s␀␀␀(␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀k␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀tuuvvwwxxyyzz{{||:    :rs=\E>\E[?1;3;4;5l\E[?7;8h:ks=\E[?1h\E=:ke=\E[?1l\E>:  :ku=\EOA:kd=\EOB:kr=\EOC:kl=\EOD:k ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀u␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀'␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀l␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀'␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀I␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀9\E[M:ip=7:dc=7\E[P:ei=\E[4l:im=\E[4h:xn:dN#30:   :do=2\E[B:co#80:li#24:cl=50\E[H\E[J:sf=2*\ED:   :le=^H:bs:am:c!␀␀␀e␀␀␀x␀␀␀p␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀4␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀=\EOP:k2=\EOQ:k3=\EOR:k4=\EOS:k5=\EOt:    :k6=\EOu:k7=\EOv:k8=\EOl:k9=\EOw:k;=\EOx:@8=\EOM:   :K1=\EOq:K2=\EOr:K3V␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀R␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀-␀␀␀3␀␀␀.␀␀␀8␀␀␀.␀␀␀2␀␀␀0␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀T␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀J␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀7␀␀␀ ␀␀␀0␀␀␀9␀␀␀:␀␀␀1␀␀␀8␀␀␀:␀␀␀1␀␀␀5␀␀␀ ␀␀␀P␀␀␀S␀␀␀T␀␀␀ ␀␀␀2␀␀␀0␀␀␀0␀␀␀3␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n:sr=^o:ll=^c:   :is=^\^r^^^s^^^d^]^w^i^s^^^]^^^o^]^w^r^i:␀swtp|ct82|southwest technical products ct82pty|psu ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-3|ibm-3278-4|ibm-3278-5|ibm-3279-2|ibm-3279-3ibm|ibm3101|3101|i3101|IBM 3101-10ibm3101h1552rv|hazeltine 1 ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀T␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀.␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀E␀␀␀M␀␀␀P␀␀␀T␀␀␀Y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀S␀␀␀T␀␀␀R␀␀␀I␀␀␀N␀␀␀G␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀7300|unixpc|pc7300|7300|3b1|Safari 4PC7300dmd620-w|att620-w|ATT620-w|620DMD-w|620MTG-w|AT&T 620 windowing t ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀m␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀.␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀M␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀B␀␀␀a␀␀␀d␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀P␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀k␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h: :   :@7=\E[4~:kD=\E[3~:kI=\E[2~:kN=\E[6~:kP=\E[5~:kh=\E[1~: :k6=\E[17~:k7=\E[18~:k8=\E[19~:k9=\E[20~:k;=\E[ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀dr:UP=\E[%dA:DO=\E[%dB:RI=\E[%dC:    :LE=\E[%dD:ct=\E[3g:st=\EH: :do=2\E[B:co#80:li#24:cl=50\E[H\E[J:sf=2*\ED:    ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀A␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀K␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀K␀␀␀o␀␀␀p␀␀␀p␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀<␀␀␀k␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀l␀␀␀@␀␀␀u␀␀␀n␀␀␀f␀␀␀i␀␀␀w␀␀␀.␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀m␀␀␀>␀␀␀ ␀␀␀I␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀e␀␀␀w␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀7:  :k0=\EOy:k1=\EOP:k2=\EOQ:k3=\EOR:k4=\EOS:k5=\EOt:   :k6=\EOu:k7=\EOv:k8=\EOl:k9=\EOw:k;=\EOx:@8=\EOM:   :K1=\ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀s␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀odel 925:  :hs:xn:am:bs:co#80:li#24:cm=\E=%+ %+ :cl=\E*:cd=\Ey:ce=\Et:is=\El\E":   :al=\EE:dl=\ER:ic=\EQ:dc=\EW ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀A␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀f␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀2621-nl|hp2621nl|2621nl|hp2621-nl|hp 2621 with no labels: :ks@:ke@:kh@:ku@:kl@:kr@:kd@:   :is=\E&j@\r:bt=\Ei ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀T␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀u␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀i␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀nd=\EC:pt:se=\E&d@:so=\E&dJ:  :us=\E&dD:ue=\E&d@:up=\EA:xs:vt#6:pb#9600:␀2621-nl|hp2621nl|2621nl|hp2621-nl|hp ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l7=red:l8=white:k6=\EP:k7=\EQ:k8=\ER:    :es:hs:ts=\Ej\Ex5\Ex1\EY8%+ \Eo:fs=\Ek\Ey5:ds=\Ey1:␀h19-us|h19us|heath ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀Q␀␀␀/␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀C␀␀␀/␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀R␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀t␀␀␀c␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀H␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀u␀␀␀r␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀p␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀with status hacked for emacssun-e|sun-nic|sune|Sun Microsystems Workstation without insert charactersun-nic ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀:␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀F2=\E[24~␀ic=\E[@␀IC=\E[%d@␀ec=\E[%dX␀   ␀al=\E[L␀dl=\E[M␀dc=\E[P␀   ␀AL=\E[%dL␀DL=\E[%dM␀DC=\E[%dP␀ ␀NP␀do=\E[ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀O␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀s␀␀␀:␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀ue=2\E[m␀   ␀md=2\E[1m␀mr=2\E[7m␀mb=2\E[5m␀me=2\E[m␀    ␀is=\E>\E[?1;3;4;5l\E[?7;8h\E[1;24r\E[24;1H␀    ␀if=/usr/s ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀k␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀DO=2\E[%dB␀RI=2\E[%dC␀   ␀LE=2\E[%dD␀ct=2\E[3g␀st=2\EH␀ta=^I␀ms␀bl=^G␀cr=^M␀eo␀it#8␀ ␀RA=\E[?7l␀SA=\E[?7h␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀o␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀i␀␀␀k␀␀␀e␀␀␀l␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀U␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀y␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀R␀␀␀E␀␀␀A␀␀␀L␀␀␀L␀␀␀Y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀d␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀g␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀m␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀u␀␀␀n␀␀␀n␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀i␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀i␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀l␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀i␀␀␀p␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀y␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀O␀␀␀F␀␀␀F␀␀␀)␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀t␀␀␀w␀␀␀e␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀k␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀D␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀l␀␀␀e␀␀␀m␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀i␀␀␀g␀␀␀h␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀T␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀l␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀x␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀5␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀_␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀ ␀␀␀u␀␀␀p␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀'␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀'␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀a␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀_␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀T␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀a␀␀␀d␀␀␀l␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀u␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀u␀␀␀r␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀g␀␀␀i␀␀␀z␀␀␀i␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀;␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀c␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀u␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀c␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀i␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀I␀␀␀ ␀␀␀k␀␀␀i␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀y␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀r␀␀␀y␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀y␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀m␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀O␀␀␀N␀␀␀L␀␀␀Y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀N␀␀␀O␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀b␀␀␀u␀␀␀g␀␀␀g␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀I␀␀␀O␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀l␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀g␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀c␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀u␀␀␀n␀␀␀)␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀1␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀x␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀u␀␀␀g␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀5␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀W␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀y␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀ ␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀R␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀'␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀k␀␀␀e␀␀␀t␀␀␀'␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀l␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀;␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀f␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀i␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀D␀␀␀o␀␀␀_␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀_␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀s␀␀␀(␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀k␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀u␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀'␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀l␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀'␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀I␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀␀␀e␀␀␀x␀␀␀p␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀4␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀V␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀R␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀-␀␀␀3␀␀␀.␀␀␀8␀␀␀.␀␀␀2␀␀␀0␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀T␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀J␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀7␀␀␀ ␀␀␀0␀␀␀9␀␀␀:␀␀␀1␀␀␀8␀␀␀:␀␀␀1␀␀␀5␀␀␀ ␀␀␀P␀␀␀S␀␀␀T␀␀␀ ␀␀␀2␀␀␀0␀␀␀0␀␀␀3␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀T␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀.␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀E␀␀␀M␀␀␀P␀␀␀T␀␀␀Y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀S␀␀␀T␀␀␀R␀␀␀I␀␀␀N␀␀␀G␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀m␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀.␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀M␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀B␀␀␀a␀␀␀d␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀P␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀k␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀A␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀K␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀K␀␀␀o␀␀␀p␀␀␀p␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀<␀␀␀k␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀l␀␀␀@␀␀␀u␀␀␀n␀␀␀f␀␀␀i␀␀␀w␀␀␀.␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀m␀␀␀>␀␀␀ ␀␀␀I␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀e␀␀␀w␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀s␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀A␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀f␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀T␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀u␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀i␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀Q␀␀␀/␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀C␀␀␀/␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀R␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀t␀␀␀c␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀H␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀u␀␀␀r␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀p␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀:␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀O␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀s␀␀␀:␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀k␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀o␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀i␀␀␀k␀␀␀e␀␀␀l␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀U␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀y␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀R␀␀␀E␀␀␀A␀␀␀L␀␀␀L␀␀␀Y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀d␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀g␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀m␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀u␀␀␀n␀␀␀n␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀i␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀i␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀l␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀i␀␀␀p␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀y␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀O␀␀␀F␀␀␀F␀␀␀)␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀t␀␀␀w␀␀␀e␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀k␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀D␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀l␀␀␀e␀␀␀m␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀i␀␀␀g␀␀␀h␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀T␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀l␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀x␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀5␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀_␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀ ␀␀␀u␀␀␀p␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀'␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀'␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀a␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀_␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀T␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀a␀␀␀d␀␀␀l␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀u␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀u␀␀␀r␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀g␀␀␀i␀␀␀z␀␀␀i␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀;␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀c␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀u␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀c␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀i␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀I␀␀␀ ␀␀␀k␀␀␀i␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀y␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀e␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀r␀␀␀y␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀y␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀m␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀O␀␀␀N␀␀␀L␀␀␀Y␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀N␀␀␀O␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀b␀␀␀u␀␀␀g␀␀␀g␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀I␀␀␀O␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀l␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀g␀␀␀h␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀c␀␀␀r␀␀␀i␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀u␀␀␀n␀␀␀)␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀1␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀l␀␀␀p␀␀␀d␀␀␀_␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀_␀␀␀s␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀r␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀x␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀m␀␀␀e␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀i␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀t␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀m␀␀␀a␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀u␀␀␀g␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀u␀␀␀m␀␀␀b␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀(␀␀␀d␀␀␀e␀␀␀f␀␀␀a␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀t␀␀␀ ␀␀␀n␀␀␀o␀␀␀w␀␀␀ ␀␀␀5␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀W␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀y␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀ ␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀R␀␀␀,␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀L␀␀␀P␀␀␀D␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀f␀␀␀o␀␀␀r␀␀␀k␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀ ␀␀␀'␀␀␀s␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀k␀␀␀e␀␀␀t␀␀␀'␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀l␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀p␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀;␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀v␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀s␀␀␀i␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀a␀␀␀f␀␀␀t␀␀␀e␀␀␀r␀␀␀ ␀␀␀r␀␀␀e␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀i␀␀␀v␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀g␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀w␀␀␀o␀␀␀u␀␀␀l␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀c␀␀␀a␀␀␀l␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀D␀␀␀o␀␀␀_␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀_␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀s␀␀␀(␀␀␀)␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀o␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀a␀␀␀k␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀␀u␀␀␀t␀␀␀i␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀o␀␀␀f␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀'␀␀␀h␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀l␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀j␀␀␀o␀␀␀b␀␀␀s␀␀␀ ␀␀␀i␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀t␀␀␀h␀␀␀e␀␀␀ ␀␀␀s␀␀␀p␀␀␀o␀␀␀o␀␀␀l␀␀␀ ␀␀␀q␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀u␀␀␀e␀␀␀'␀␀␀ ␀␀␀p␀␀␀r␀␀␀o␀␀␀c␀␀␀e␀␀␀s␀␀␀s␀␀␀.␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀I␀␀␀n␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀␀␀e␀␀␀x␀␀␀p␀␀␀a␀␀␀n␀␀␀d␀␀␀ ␀␀␀-␀␀␀4␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀    become the 'handle the jobs' process. Similarly, when an lpc operation needs ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀    to start a 'handle the jobs' process,  a message is sent to the LPD server ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀a␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀A␀␀␀␀␀␀}n␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀h_(␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀OO␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀`␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀r␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀f␀␀␀␀␀␀&␀␀␀&␀␀␀&2@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀L))O␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀*"c␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀\%␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀}␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀}]j␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀j␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀I␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀
␀␀␀ifo␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀j␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀Q␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀w␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀5␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀K;|␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀<\␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀]␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀T␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀pI␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀   8␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀7␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀I␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀)=g␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀w ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀w&t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀-]i␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀J,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀ ␀␀␀wh␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀␀␀!␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀"␀␀␀"␀␀␀x␀␀␀␀␀␀#␀␀␀#␀␀␀T␀␀␀␀␀␀$␀␀␀$␀␀␀H␀␀␀␀␀␀%␀␀␀%␀␀␀u␀␀␀␀␀␀'␀␀␀'␀␀␀V,␀␀␀␀␀␀(␀␀␀(␀␀␀x␀␀␀␀␀␀)␀␀␀)␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀␀*␀␀␀*␀␀␀"␀␀␀␀␀␀+␀␀␀+␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀expand -4␀ added; 6513 lines deleted
t get overloaded as easily.ueswings totooto do this work.  Similarly, the the␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀r␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀o␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀l␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀i␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@p /   K␀␀␀K␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀p␀p␀@K␀␀␀K␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀q@pp4␀␀␀4␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀        enough so that the other scripts could run).␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@qp␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀q␀q@H␀␀␀H␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀q@q␀AP␀␀␀P␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@rq␀r$␀␀␀$␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀        number of processes at once.␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀rq␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀r@r␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀srAE␀␀␀E␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@sr␀BG␀␀␀G␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀sBC␀␀␀C␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t@ss@␀␀␀@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀   duties of the 'handle the jobs in the spool queue' process.  Ints@t@␀␀␀@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀   this version the 'service socket' process sends a 'start queue'␀u␀tt@␀␀␀@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀   request to the LPD server and then exits.  The LPD service willut@u=␀␀␀=␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀   then fork a process to become the 'handle the jobs' process.␀␀␀u␀u␀CD␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀vuCD␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@vu␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀v␀v␀DC␀␀␀C␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀v@vDD␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀wv␀EC␀␀␀C␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀wv@w@␀␀␀@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ much easier,  and the system does not get overloaded as easily.w␀w␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀xwEB␀␀␀B␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@xw ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀x␀x␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀x@x␀FC␀␀␀C␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀yxFD␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀yx@y"␀␀␀"␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀     LPD process looking for work.␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀y␀y␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@zy␀z2␀␀␀2␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀  Keith ("HP Printer Dies Horrible Death") Rinaldo␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀zy␀GA␀␀␀A␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀z@zGB␀␀␀B␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@{z␀{@␀␀␀@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀  error message on the printer console such as 7900FE.  The IFHP{z␀HH␀␀␀H␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀|@{{@␀␀␀@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀  TCP/IP facility does not solve this problem,  as sometimes the@|{HD␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀|␀||@␀␀␀@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀  is non-functional.  You need to try to get a response from the@}@|␀}/␀␀␀/␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀3  printer,  which is what the IFHP filter does.ftp␀/nonexistent␀}|␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀sten␀~@}}?␀␀␀?␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀/usr  NOTE: send_job_rw_timeout default value is now 0 (no timeout) @~}␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀~␀~␀IH␀␀␀H␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀~@~@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ol/c␀~␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ews @~IF␀␀␀F␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀Game␀@␀␀␀@␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀    network (or parallel port or serial port) connection will be␀P@␀JG␀␀␀G␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀o␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀a␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀r␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀h␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀p␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀r␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀o␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀c␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀.␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀   ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀d␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀o␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀a␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀r␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀a␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀q␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀u␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀u␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀'␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀;␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀'␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀h␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀a␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀n␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀d␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀l␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀h␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀j␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀o␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀b␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀'␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀p␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀r␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀o␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀c␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀i␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀h␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀a␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀m␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀a␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀g␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀i␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀n␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀o␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀h␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀L␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀P␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀s␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀r␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀v␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀r␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀papowell␀*␀␀Patrick Powell␀/home/papowell␀/bin/csh␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀0   ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀$$dp(p 4L<,pd|,X@H␀x4hP␀`L|d|l`P<<lD8l H

`

   t   L   @   l`|0`T␀d\|,pd|pd$8␀␀␀␀␀␀Version LPRng-3.8.17 - Sat Oct 26 20:11:28 PDT 2002␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀I␀␀␀␀␀␀  for such cases as the system will die a horrible death at startup.␀␀I␀␀␀␀␀␀  parameters, such as user processes.  Added limit of 1024 processes␀␀A␀␀␀␀␀␀  Some Linux distributions set 'unlimited' resources for all␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀  delivery of jobs.␀␀␀H␀␀␀␀␀␀  get delivered in order A B C.  For users who MUST have sequential␀␀␀E␀␀␀␀␀␀  job at a time in FIFO order.  If you send jobs A B C then they␀␀J␀␀␀␀␀␀  Added the 'fifo' option  - this now makes LPRng handle one incoming␀7␀␀␀␀␀␀Version LPRng-3.8.18 - Mon Dec 2 12:08:34 PST 2002␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀F␀␀␀␀␀␀  by Keith ("Wanna bet on that?") Rinaldo <rinaldok@egr.unlv.edu>␀F␀␀␀␀
