    Fixed up a lot of minor portab  After much consideration, added the 'client.xxx' and 'server.xxx'ixed fumble in gethostinfo.c
    - will die if it cannot find  client.xxx or server.xxx then this can be used to set the correspondingl instead of dying later.

    Fixup the the TESTSUPPOR  entry to be used for both client and server operation, especially to make sure that you have GNU Make.  This
    appears to be  in situations where the lpd server is forwarding or sending jobsl 17 10:57:49 PDT 1995 Patrick Powell

    ********* BSDI ****  Added SSL authentication.  See the README.SSL.SECURITY file forwed, fixed or modified.  The 'snprintf' function
    was rename  the truly complicated details.  Note that testing with certificatessnprintf functions.  Fixed up some questionable
    uses of               && (s = Find_str_value(header_info,AUTHUSER,Value_sep)) ){iour in strncat(),  and fixed up its uses.  Strncpy
                  DEBUG1("Check_for_missing_files: authuser '%s'", s ); where possible.

